title: Cutie Honey - The Another
description:
Manga adaptation of the anime Cutie Honey done by Ken Ishikawa and Yuu Okazaki, it follows more the anime and the character design is closer than the Go Nagai manga.

The Cutie Honey manga written and drawn by Yuu Okazaki originally published in Nakayoshi based on the 70's anime.

Act 1-8=Yuu Okazaki's version
Act 9-19=Ken Ishikawa's version
